Commentary Text: Tushar Deshpande to Karthik, out Caught by Theekshana!! "Theekshana finally takes a catch," say my colleagues Nikhil and Saurabh in unison. 141kph, low full toss outside off, Karthik shuffles across to slogsweep. Doesn't generate sufficient power behind it and hits it straight to the fielder at cow corner. Theekshana, who dropped two catches, holds onto this one. He punches the air in delight. Karthik c Theekshana b Tushar Deshpande 28(14) [4s-3 6s-1]

Commentary Text: Theekshana to Maxwell, out Caught by Dhoni!! That's gone a mile up, Dhoni asks Theekshana not to come close to the ball, settles under the skier and safely gobbles it up. Out comes the bow and arrow celebration from Theekshana. It's the carrom ball from Theekshana at 104.2kph, and Maxwell looked to slog-sweep it away. Ended up slicing it a long way up in the air. End of a fantastic knock from Maxwell, though! Dhoni had a chat with the umpire after the wicket, think it had something to do with the spider cam. Maxwell c Dhoni b Theekshana 76(36) [4s-3 6s-8]
